{"tid":1410653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工後更需要一個感謝運動","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:44:06.000Z","uid":160844,"like":111,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"668f620982524bb5847d3875d706cc3f438ba1d6","tid":1410653,"uid":160844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"罷工後需要一個道歉運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1410110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1410110</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完有感而發<br />\n各位，需要道歉嘅，係極權政府同警察。<br />\n我地更加需要支持同鼓勵一眾努力不懈，同心協力嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n大家都係香港人，<br />\n希望各位喺今日罷工集會時或今日之後，<br />\n向各位有份參加同支持罷工嘅香港人，<br />\n表達謝意，希望各位香港人可以一齊行落去。<br />\n<br />\n面對暴政，絕不妥協。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家無私地支持罷工<br />\n多謝大家為我地嘅地方一同出一分力<br />\n多謝各位同路人<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"20fbbcc0d5c2bedecb6f9e20fef0ef26ab9b56ff","tid":1410653,"uid":22465,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"罷工後需要另一個罷工運動"},{"pid":"b561e230255fbf7cd4561e001362f6a8916d961c","tid":1410653,"uid":160844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0e8c801c17e0f14a5274f5878c2e993b57d2932e","tid":1410653,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"ddb34da2aedfcb8814b16cfeef4e47c0c9a30b91","tid":1410653,"uid":160844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"68ea6863ea60b76ae478c328be2bdaee2aa82583","tid":1410653,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"感覺ok,留名睇埋風向先"},{"pid":"0df67f881e404e10986c318d543cafce5a77a422","tid":1410653,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17238043b19da2f06ad8be6ef9b538827aa33410","tid":1410653,"uid":160844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2